lead_paragraph: A team led by Dr. Joshua D. Stephany, Orange County’s chief medical examiner, has conducted autopsies on all of the 49 victims of the attack at the Pulse.

headline.print_headline: Almost Too Many Autopsies to Count
headline.main: Orlando Medical Examiner: ‘Take a Typical Homicide Scene, Multiply It by 50’

snippet: A team led by Dr. Joshua D. Stephany, Orange County’s chief medical examiner, has conducted autopsies on all of the 49 victims of the attack at the Pulse.
abstract: Orlando, Fla, chief medical examiner Joshua D Stephany describes scene inside Pulse nightclub in aftermath of mass shooting; Stephany and his staff have conducted 49 autopsies in days since slaughter.
